Hysterical theories or not, one thing we can all agree on is that none of this can be explained by conventional science.  While you describe the theories presented in the documentary as "hysterical", conventional science's theories to explain these phenomena is thin at best.  I think the best thing about this is that it will open you're mind to new ways of looking at the world.  Unless you are a stubborn know-it-all, then this would just piss you off.
